<div id="ctr"> <div id="hd"> <h1> Neuroscience For Kids </h1> </div>	

<div id="mn"> <h2> privacy </h2>

<h3><a href="newslet.html">Neuroscience Newsletter</a></h3> 

<p> Neuroscience for Kids does NOT collect any personal information about the people who
use the web site other than e-mail addresses of people who request the
monthly newsletter. </p>  

<p> Although we would like to know if the people who
request the newsletter are students, teachers or parents, this information
is not required and you are under no obligation to provide this
information.  </p>

<p> Furthermore, your name, phone number and home address are
not needed.  Children under 13 years of age should get permission
from their parents before they subscribe to the newsletter. </p>

<hr /> 

<h3><a href="hunt10.html">Treasure Hunt</a></h3>

<p> Only your first name and last initial are required for your name to be
added to the <a href="gna11.html">Golden Neuron Award</a> page. If you
like, you can include your city or school, but this is not required.  
Your phone number and home address are not needed.  Children under 13
years of age should get permission from their parents before they apply
for a Golden Neuron Award.</p>

